		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I think I read that leaving it floating either makes it work only on snesses with enabled lockouts (wether it be pal or ntsc) and connecting it to 5v makes it only work on disabled lockouts or the other way around.
<br />
<br />edit: did you 60 hz mod your snes? I recall reading the game needs to be running in 60 hz or it'll complain. (but only on some carts iirc)

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


